# Hugging Face token — required for downloading gated models (e.g. FLUX.1-schnell)
# 1. Accept terms at https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-schnell
# 2. Create a token at https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens (Read access is enough)
# 3. Copy this file to .env and paste your token below
HF_TOKEN=hf_your_token_here
